The water we drink, our health insurance.

677
00:36:41,940 --> 00:36:43,630
Even if we did, would it matter?

678
00:36:45,170 --> 00:36:48,400
You know, if our only option is Blue Cross or Blue Shield,

679
00:36:48,490 --> 00:36:50,820
what the f--- is the difference?

680
00:36:56,290 --> 00:36:58,270
In fact, aren't they-- aren't they the same?

681
00:37:01,040 --> 00:37:02,080
No, man...

682
