00:37:55,560 --> 00:37:57,190
You've brought up this issue before,

696
00:37:58,220 --> 00:38:00,560
this issue of not feeling like you're in control.

697
00:38:00,560 --> 00:38:01,610
Do you remember?

698
00:38:05,410 --> 00:38:06,960
When we spoke about your father.

699
00:38:08,250 --> 00:38:10,550
You talked about how he chose to do nothing

