00:38:18,720 --> 00:38:21,070
He could have sought better care than what he was getting.

704
00:38:22,040 --> 00:38:23,530
Instead, he did nothing.

705
00:38:26,060 --> 00:38:29,770
Maybe your father felt the same way as you do now.

706
00:38:30,820 --> 00:38:33,870
After all, like you said, what's the point?

707
00:38:33,900 --> 00:38:35,630
- It's different. - What's different

708
00:38:36,140 --> 00:38:39,110
is you've found options, Elliot.

709
00:38:39,270 --> 00:38:42,510
That's the power you have. That's the control you own.

710
00:38:42,510 --> 00:38:45,380
You don't have to just take what life gives you.

711
00:38:47,100 --> 00:38:48,000
Come on.

712
00:38:48,650 --> 00:38:51,440
Tell me what is going on with you.

