00:38:58,770 --> 00:39:00,080
Shut up!

716
00:39:03,250 --> 00:39:04,790
You've got bags under your eyes.

717
00:39:04,830 --> 00:39:06,780
You're yelling. You're jittery.

718
00:39:06,780 --> 00:39:08,820
For the last month, I have seen you

